{"type": "article", "id": 24533, "title": "雨伞锁", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-28T06:04:40Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 63, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160703120030T4n08fyuZzqF5hkA.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">雨伞也许是最容易丢失的生活用品之一，这几个中国设计师在雨伞的把手上设计了密码锁。仅仅是在弯曲把手的最外面安装一个可伸缩的密码锁，需要时将它拔出来形成一个闭合环，类似自行车车锁，简易且方便。产品目前还没上市。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120029jeO4xd6TzFo9w8uW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.76095238\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120029h9DT4WogqtyGax27.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.33428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}